    "education-environment-title": "Educating Youth on Environmental Awareness",
    "education-environment-description": "We consider environmental education for youth fundamental for a sustainable future. We create and support programs that raise awareness and inform young people about environmental issues, encouraging the development of ecological consciousness and the adoption of responsible practices for environmental protection.",
    "education-conferences-title": "Organizing Scientific Conferences and Events",
    "education-conferences-description": "We organize conferences and events focusing on scientific topics, including environmental sciences. These gatherings serve as a platform for presenting research, exchanging ideas, and discussing the latest developments, promoting scientific dialogue and knowledge dissemination.",
    "tech-title": "Technology",
